body.description: Make organization fun and easy with the BIC Brite Liner Highlighters Assorted Colors. These highlighters have a chisel tip for broad highlighting or fine underlining, making them perfect for highlighting school or office documents. BIC's highlighter markers use translucent ink to emphasize what's important on the page without obscuring the text below. Reliable and long-lasting, each BIC Brite Liner highlighter writes for up to eight hours without a cap and does not dry out, so you can work with confidence. The convenient pen-shaped design lets you easily grip and comfortably use the highlighters to organize your notes or underline passages in textbooks, notebooks and documents. Looking for classic highlighters for journals or assorted color marker sets for adults? BIC Brite Liner Multicolor Highlighters add a fun pop of flair to your art, office or school supplies. Each pack contains 12 chisel tip highlighter markers in the following assorted colors: yellow, pink, blue, green and orange. BIC highlighters are ACMI-approved for a high-quality, safe product you can trust. Whether you're emphasizing text or just feel like getting creative, choose BIC Brite Liner Highlighters.

Make Highlighting Fun with BIC Brite Liner! Super-Bright, Fluorescent Ink Available in five super-bright colors yellow, pink, orange, green, and blue BIC Brite Liner Highlighters allow you to easily color-code your notes and documents. Versatile, Firm Chisel Tip Each BIC Brite Liner Highlighter features a reliable chisel tip that creates both thick and thin lines with ease. You’ll be able to toggle between broad highlighting and fine underlining with just a twist of the wrist. Resists Drying Out BIC Brite Liner Highlighters won't dry out* when the cap is left off for up to eight hours, so you can use them for extended periods of time without having to switch to another highlighter. *when the cap is left off up to 8 hours

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Bright and just right
reviews.reviewText: The BIC Brite Liner Highlighters, with their chisel tip and vibrant colors, have become my preferred choice for highlighting and organizing information. This 12-count pack offers a variety of colors, making it a versatile addition to my office supplies.What sets these highlighters apart is the chisel tip, providing both broad and fine highlighting options. Whether I'm emphasizing key points in a document or underlining important details, the BIC Brite Liners offer precision and control.The colors are bright and eye-catching, adding a touch of vibrancy to my notes. The ink dries quickly, preventing smudging and allowing for neat and organized highlighting.Durability is another positive aspect; these highlighters withstand extended use without drying out quickly. The clear caps ensure that the ink remains fresh for each use.For those seeking a reliable and cost-effective set of highlighters, the BIC Brite Liners are a fantastic choice. They combine functionality with a burst of color, making the process of highlighting and organizing information an enjoyable task. Highly recommended for students, professionals, or anyone who values quality in their writing instruments.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars You can't go wrong with this brand of highlighters.
reviews.reviewText: I like this brand of highlighters. They are always reliable and last a long time. I have small hands so they fit well and don't make my hand tired from long uses. I think the tip is a perfect size as it highlights just the right amount of text. Not too big or too small. I would purchase these again.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars great for school, but not good for blacklight
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this product for a glow party for kids to color under a blacklight. Unfortunatley this brand does not glow under a blacklight. While it works for its intended use, I wanted to let others know in case they too were looking specifically for highlighters that will glow under a blacklight.
